    <title type="html"><![CDATA[How to Install Octopress on Github]]></title>
    <link href="http://andystu.github.io/blog/2014/12/16/how-to-install-octopress-on-github/"/>
    <updated>2014-12-16T00:17:53+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://andystu.github.io/blog/2014/12/16/how-to-install-octopress-on-github</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>在Github上使用octopress建構blog</h2>

<h3>1. on mac</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ cd ~/.ssh
</span><span class='line'>$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "xxx@xxx.xxx.xx"
</span><span class='line'>$ pbcopy &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub #copy pubkey to clipboard</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>2. on Github</h3>

<p>github 申請帳號 (e.g. xxxx)<br/>
github 建立 xxxx.github.io 的repository<br/>
github <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/generating-ssh-keys/">上傳ssh key</a></p>

<!--more-->


<h3>3. back to mac</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ ssh -T git@github.com #for testing your sshkey</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>4. Local端 安裝octopress</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ git clone git://github.com/imathis/octopress.git octopress
</span><span class='line'>$ cd octopress
</span><span class='line'>$ bundle install
</span><span class='line'>$ rake install
</span><span class='line'>$ rake setup_github_pages</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>trouble shooting</h3>

<ul>
<li>problem during &ldquo;rake deploy&rdquo;
在 rake deploy 會出現 error, 解決方法如下</li>
<li>編輯 Rakefile (Edit the Rakefile and look for this line:)</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>system "git push origin #{deploy_branch}"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>修改成</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>system "git push origin +#{deploy_branch}"</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>其他解法</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd octopress/_deploy
</span><span class='line'>git pull origin master
</span><span class='line'>cd ..
</span><span class='line'>rake deploy</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>Don&rsquo;t forget git it</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>$ git add .
</span><span class='line'>$ git commit -m 'xxxxx'
</span><span class='line'>$ git push origin source</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>Done and Ready to blog</li>
</ul>

]]></content>
